{% comment %}
  Homepage del portal B2B LedsC4 Outlet.

  Dos ramas según customer state:

  1. Customer aprobado (.b2b-aprobado-home)
     Dashboard claro: hero corto con saludo personalizado + grid de
     colecciones (linklists.main-menu) con fallback a "Ver catálogo
     completo" + CTA destacado a "Mis solicitudes". Se renderiza con el
     header simplificado del snippet b2b-header-aprobado y el
     footer-group de Dawn (ambos via theme.liquid).

  2. Anónimo / pendiente / rechazado (.b2b-portal)
     Hero oscuro full-screen con features y footer legal. Diseño estable
     desde 2026-04-19 — mismo mensaje para anon, pendiente y rechazado.
     Sin header (theme.liquid lo suprime en index para esta rama). El
     footer legal local sustituye al footer-group de Dawn (que solo se
     renderiza para aprobados).
{% endcomment %}

{%- if customer.tags contains 'aprobado' -%}

  {%- comment -%}
    Cascade fallback con clave i18n al final: si empresa y first_name son blank,
    cae al string literal 'ledsc4.common.greeting.fallback_bienvenido' que el filtro `| t`
    final traduce a "Bienvenido". Cuando empresa o first_name tienen valor, `| t`
    devuelve la propia string (Shopify behavior: si la key no existe, retorna input).
  {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- assign saludo = customer.metafields.b2b.empresa
    | default: customer.first_name
    | default: 'ledsc4.common.greeting.fallback_bienvenido' | t
  -%}

  <section class="b2b-aprobado-home" aria-labelledby="b2b-aprobado-heading">

    <div class="b2b-aprobado-home__hero">
      <p class="b2b-aprobado-home__eyebrow">{{ 'ledsc4.common.eyebrow.portal_b2b' | t }}</p>
      <h1 id="b2b-aprobado-heading" class="b2b-aprobado-home__heading">
        {{ 'ledsc4.common.greeting.hola_name' | t: name: saludo }}
      </h1>
      <p class="b2b-aprobado-home__lead">
        {{ 'ledsc4.aprobado_home.lead' | t }}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="b2b-aprobado-home__grid-wrap">
      {%- render 'b2b-dashboard-cards' -%}
    </div>

    <div class="b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes">
      <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}pages/mis-solicitudes" class="b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-card">
        <div class="b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-text">
          <p class="b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-eyebrow">{{ 'ledsc4.aprobado_home.solicitudes.eyebrow' | t }}</p>
          <h3 class="b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-title">{{ 'ledsc4.aprobado_home.solicitudes.title' | t }}</h3>
          <p class="b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-desc">
            {{ 'ledsc4.aprobado_home.solicitudes.desc' | t }}
          </p>
        </div>
        <span class="b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>

  {% style %}
    .b2b-aprobado-home {
      --b2b-accent: rgb(var(--color-link));
      --b2b-radius: 14px;
      --b2b-radius-sm: 10px;

      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      font-family: var(--font-ledsc4-body);
      color: rgb(var(--color-foreground));
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .b2b-aprobado-home *,
    .b2b-aprobado-home *::before,
    .b2b-aprobado-home *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .b2b-aprobado-home__hero {
      min-height: 28vh;
      max-height: 42vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.08);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .b2b-aprobado-home__eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-ledsc4-ui);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.6);
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }
    .b2b-aprobado-home__heading {
      font-family: var(--font-ledsc4-heading);
      font-size: clamp(4rem, 6vw, 6.4rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin: 0 0 1.125rem;
      color: rgb(var(--color-foreground));
    }
    .b2b-aprobado-home__lead {
      font-family: var(--font-ledsc4-body);
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 1.8vw, 2.1rem);
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.72);
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 60ch;
    }

    /* GRID — los estilos viven en snippets/b2b-dashboard-cards.liquid */
    .b2b-aprobado-home__grid-wrap {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    /* SOLICITUDES CTA — visualmente distinto al grid */
    .b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: rgb(var(--color-button));
      color: rgb(var(--color-button-text));
      border-radius: var(--b2b-radius);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }
    .b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.14);
    }
    .b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-ledsc4-ui);
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      opacity: 0.7;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    }
    .b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-title {
      font-family: var(--font-ledsc4-heading);
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 3vw, 3.4rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      margin: 0 0 0.625rem;
      color: rgb(var(--color-button-text));
    }
    .b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-desc {
      font-family: var(--font-ledsc4-body);
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      opacity: 0.85;
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 60ch;
    }
    .b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-arrow {
      font-size: 3.2rem;
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .b2b-aprobado-home {
        padding: 1.75rem 1rem 3rem;
      }
      .b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-card {
        padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
      }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .b2b-aprobado-home__solicitudes-card {
        transition: none;
      }
    }
  {% endstyle %}

{%- else -%}

  {%- comment -%}
    Rama no-aprobado: anónimo, pendiente o rechazado. Layout estable desde
    2026-04-19 — NO modificar sin revisar todo el flujo de marketing.
  {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="b2b-portal" aria-labelledby="b2b-portal-heading">

    <div class="b2b-portal__hero">
      <header class="b2b-portal__brand">
        {%- if shop.brand.logo != blank -%}
          <img
            src="{{ shop.brand.logo | image_url: width: 400 }}"
            alt="{{ shop.name | escape }}"
            width="180"
            height="auto"
            loading="eager"
          >
        {%- elsif section.settings.logo != blank -%}
          <img
            src="{{ section.settings.logo | image_url: width: 400 }}"
            alt="{{ shop.name | escape }}"
            width="{{ section.settings.logo_width | default: 180 }}"
            height="auto"
            loading="eager"
          >
        {%- else -%}
          <span class="b2b-portal__brand-wordmark">LEDS C4 <em>Outlet</em></span>
        {%- endif -%}
      </header>

      <div class="b2b-portal__hero-body">
        <p class="b2b-portal__eyebrow">{{ 'ledsc4.portal.eyebrow' | t }}</p>
        <h1 id="b2b-portal-heading" class="b2b-portal__heading">
          {{ 'ledsc4.portal.heading_html' | t }}
        </h1>
        <p class="b2b-portal__lead">
          {{ 'ledsc4.portal.lead' | t }}
        </p>
        <div class="b2b-portal__ctas">
          {%- comment -%}
            Opción C (Fase D post-launch): pasamos checkout_url para que
            Shopify new customer accounts redirija a nuestra page tras
            login, en vez de a shopify.com/<shop>/account.
          {%- endcomment -%}
          <a href="/customer_authentication/login?return_to=%2Fpages%2Fmis-solicitudes" class="b2b-portal__btn b2b-portal__btn--primary">
            {{ 'ledsc4.common.cta.login' | t }}
          </a>
          <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}pages/acceso-profesional#registro" class="b2b-portal__btn b2b-portal__btn--secondary">
            {{ 'ledsc4.common.cta.solicitar_acceso' | t }}
          </a>
        </div>
        <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}pages/acceso-profesional" class="b2b-portal__help-link">
          {{ 'ledsc4.portal.help_link' | t }}
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="b2b-portal__scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
        <span>{{ 'ledsc4.portal.scroll_hint' | t }}</span>
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"/></svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="b2b-portal__features">
      <div class="b2b-portal__features-grid">
        <article class="b2b-portal__feature">
          <svg class="b2b-portal__feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
          <h3>{{ 'ledsc4.portal.f1_title' | t }}</h3>
          <p>{{ 'ledsc4.portal.f1_desc' | t }}</p>
        </article>

        <article class="b2b-portal__feature">
          <svg class="b2b-portal__feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          <h3>{{ 'ledsc4.portal.f2_title' | t }}</h3>
          <p>{{ 'ledsc4.portal.f2_desc' | t }}</p>
        </article>

        <article class="b2b-portal__feature">
          <svg class="b2b-portal__feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
          <h3>{{ 'ledsc4.portal.f3_title' | t }}</h3>
          <p>{{ 'ledsc4.portal.f3_desc' | t }}</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="b2b-portal__footer">
      <nav class="b2b-portal__footer-nav" aria-label="{{ 'ledsc4.common.footer.aria_legal' | t }}">
        <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}pages/aviso-legal">{{ 'ledsc4.common.footer.aviso_legal' | t }}</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}pages/politica-de-privacidad">{{ 'ledsc4.common.footer.privacidad' | t }}</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}pages/condiciones-de-uso">{{ 'ledsc4.common.footer.condiciones' | t }}</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}pages/canal-de-denuncias">{{ 'ledsc4.common.footer.canal_etico' | t }}</a>
      </nav>
      <p class="b2b-portal__footer-note">
        {%- assign current_year = 'now' | date: '%Y' -%}
        {{ 'ledsc4.common.footer.copyright_html' | t: year: current_year }}
      </p>
    </footer>

  </section>

  <style>
    .b2b-portal {
      --bg: #0c0e12;
      --bg-alt: #14171c;
      --fg: #f5f5f7;
      --fg-muted: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.68);
      --fg-dim: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.45);
      --accent: #d4a84a;
      --border: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.08);

      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--fg);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .b2b-portal *,
    .b2b-portal *::before,
    .b2b-portal *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .b2b-portal__hero {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      position: relative;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 1px);
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(212, 168, 74, 0.08), transparent 60%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--bg-alt) 100%);
    }

    .b2b-portal__brand {
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    .b2b-portal__brand img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
    }

    .b2b-portal__brand-wordmark {
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--fg);
    }
    .b2b-portal__brand-wordmark em {
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-transform: none;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      font-size: 0.85em;
    }

    .b2b-portal__hero-body {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 680px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .b2b-portal__eyebrow {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .b2b-portal__heading {
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.6rem, 6vw, 6.4rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
      color: var(--fg);
      letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    }
    .b2b-portal__heading em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 400;
      display: block;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .b2b-portal__heading em {
        display: inline;
      }
    }

    .b2b-portal__lead {
      font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 1.8vw, 2rem);
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--fg-muted);
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
      max-width: 60ch;
    }

    .b2b-portal__ctas {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .b2b-portal__btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 16.8rem;
      padding: 1.5rem 2.8rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .b2b-portal__btn--primary {
      background: var(--fg);
      color: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--fg);
    }
    .b2b-portal__btn--primary:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--bg);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .b2b-portal__btn--secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--fg);
      border: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
    }
    .b2b-portal__btn--secondary:hover {
      border-color: var(--fg);
      background: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.04);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .b2b-portal__help-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: var(--fg-dim);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }
    .b2b-portal__help-link:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    .b2b-portal__help-link:focus-visible {
      outline: 1px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 4px;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .b2b-portal__scroll-hint {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 1.75rem;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--fg-dim);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      animation: b2b-bounce 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes b2b-bounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, 0); }
      50% { transform: translate(-50%, 6px); }
    }

    /* FEATURES */
    .b2b-portal__features {
      background: var(--bg-alt);
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .b2b-portal__features-grid {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .b2b-portal__feature {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .b2b-portal__feature-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      stroke-width: 1.25;
    }

    .b2b-portal__feature h3 {
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin: 0 0 0.625rem;
      color: var(--fg);
      letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    }

    .b2b-portal__feature p {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--fg-muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    .b2b-portal__footer {
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 2.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .b2b-portal__footer-nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.875rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
    }

    .b2b-portal__footer-nav a {
      color: var(--fg-muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }
    .b2b-portal__footer-nav a:hover {
      color: var(--fg);
    }

    .b2b-portal__footer-note {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: var(--fg-dim);
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .b2b-portal__btn,
      .b2b-portal__scroll-hint {
        transition: none;
        animation: none;
      }
    }
  </style>

{%- endif -%}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "B2B Portal Home",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section-b2b-portal",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Branding"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "logo",
      "label": "Logo (fallback)",
      "info": "Se usa si Online Store > Brand > Logo está vacío. Fondo transparente; blanco sobre hero oscuro."
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "logo_width",
      "label": "Ancho del logo (px)",
      "min": 80,
      "max": 320,
      "step": 10,
      "default": 180
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "B2B Portal Home"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
